## 🔍 How It Works

1. Read healthcare data (FHIR JSON)
2. Group records by patient ID
3. Derive encryption key dynamically
4. Encrypt data using AES-GCM
5. Generate hash using SHA-256
6. Store hash on blockchain
7. Store encrypted data off-chain
8. Verify and decrypt during access

